<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: #f6f6f6; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 10px;" width="100%">
	
		<tr>
			<td align="center" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff; width: 600px;">
				
					<tr>
						<td style="padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff;"><img alt="Alliance Rural &amp; Remote - Email header (2)" src="https://allianceaustralia--uat.sandbox.file.force.com/file-asset-public/Alliance_Rural_Remote_Email_heade?oid=00DAD00000BK4sL" style="max-width: 683.05px" title="Alliance Rural &amp; Remote - Email header (2)" /><a href="https://www.alliancenursing.com.au"> </a></td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td style="height: 30px;">&nbsp;</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td align="left" style="padding: 0 45px;">
						<p style="font-size:12px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;"><span style="color:#e67e22;"><strong>PLEASE NOTE:</strong> Your contract with NSW will not be accepted or processed until your application paperwork attached is approved through NSW HR.</span><br />
						&nbsp;</p>

						<p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},<br />
						<br />
						Attached is the paperwork, that you need to complete and return to us as soon as possible, for your contract at<br />
						«FacilityName»,&nbsp;«HealthServiceDistrict». Under the NSW Health Agreement, this pack should cover all Health Districts.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						We need urgently:</p>

						<ul>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">NSW Working With Children Clearance&nbsp;OR&nbsp;proof of application you can apply for this <a href="https://www.service.nsw.gov.au/transaction/apply-for-a-working-with-children-check">here</a>.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">NDIS Clearance – <span style="color:#e74c3c;">to be sent separately – check if this location requires this.</span>&nbsp;</li>
						</ul>

						<p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">Immunisation Information – If we have your Immunisations and Serology on file&nbsp;we can send this through, but you&nbsp;must&nbsp;complete the attached forms.<br />
						<br />
						We&nbsp;also need evidence of a recent Flu vaccination &amp; COVID Vaccination Evidence. Please note the attached mandatory training requirements for NSW Health.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						If you plan to work in other areas, please don’t date any forms APART from the Statutory Declarations.&nbsp;This may save you some additional time later on, BUT you will still need to review and confirm any details on previous forms.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						Please complete the below:</p>

						<ul>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Agency Nurse &amp; Midwife Onboarding Checklist, please complete and sign this form.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Travel Request form&nbsp;– <span style="color:#e74c3c;">delete if not applicable</span></li>
						</ul>

						<p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">&nbsp;<br />
						Agency Nursing &amp; Midwife Onboarding forms has been broken down for you:</p>

						<ol>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Undertaking/Declaration form, page 5, please complete.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Tuberculosis&nbsp;Assessment form, pages 6-8, please complete.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Model&nbsp;Health Declaration, page 9, please complete and tick the appropriate box.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Drugs&nbsp;of Addiction form, page 10, please sign.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Code&nbsp;of Conduct form, page 11, please sign – the entire code of conduct is attached separately for you to read.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">List of appendices attached for your information – page 12</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Statutory&nbsp;Declaration of Hours, page 13, please complete ONLY if you need to provide hours for what you have worked Overseas&nbsp;and have this witnessed – This will ONLY&nbsp;be accepted in that instance, please provide updated statements of service if you need to provide more hours to increase your current nursing level.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Vaccination&nbsp;Record Card, pages 14-16, please complete ONLY&nbsp;if you need to – we will provide the evidence on file – please ensure you have provided all your updated information.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Hepatitis&nbsp;B Vaccine Declaration, page 17 – only to be completed if you haven’t provided evidence of vaccinations – this must be signed by an authorised person – if you have the evidence and haven’t provided this, please send it through.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Statutory&nbsp;Declaration form, page 18-19, please complete in its entirety&nbsp;(including your address and occupation)&nbsp;and have this witnessed by the appropriate person listed on page 19.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">10 Hour Waiver Form, page 20, please complete.</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Overseas&nbsp;Statutory Declaration, page 21 – ONLY to be completed if you were born overseas, please complete (including your address and occupation)&nbsp;and have this witnessed by an appropriate person.</li>
						</ol>

						<p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;"><strong>To set up your ROB Profile</strong><br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						How to Create a ROB Portal - Instructions</p>

						<ol>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Go to NSW Health –&nbsp;ROB Portal</li>
							<li style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 10px 0px 20px;">Select “new user”</li>
						</ol>

						<p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">For further assistance or to report a technical issue, please contact the HCM Customer Experience Helpdesk on 1300 679 367 (Option 3).<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						PLEASE EMAIL COMPLETED PAPERWORK TO<br />
						candidatemanagement@allianceruralremote.com.au&nbsp;as soon as possible.<br />
						<br />
						If there are any questions, please don’t hesitate to contact me on the number below.</p>

						<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; border: none; border-collapse: collapse;">
							
								<tr>
									<td align="center" bgcolor="#007DC3" style="background-color: #007DC3; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px;"><a href="https://allianceaustralia--uat.sandbox.my.salesforce-sites.com/onboarding/apex/b3o__MyDocuments?id={{{Recipient.Id}}}&amp;sessionKey={{{Recipient.Session_Key__c}}}" style="display: inline-block; font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">OPEN THE ALLIANCE PORTAL</a></td>
								</tr>
							
						</table>

						<p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;"><br />
						Kind regards,<br />
						Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health</p>
						</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td style="height: 20px;">&nbsp;</td>
